where formula_24 are three orthonormal unit basis vectors, and if the principal stresses formula_25 are aligned with the basis vectors formula_26, then the expressions for formula_27 are
:formula_28
The Mohr–Coulomb failure criterion can then be evaluated using the usual expression
formula_29
for the six planes of maximum shear stress.

