<text>Faliscan may refer to:

*Falisci, an ancient Italic people
*Faliscan language</text><links>
<link wikidata="Q253482" start="25" end="32" title="Falisci" label="Falisci"/>
<link wikidata="Q35669" start="60" end="77" title="Faliscan language" label="Faliscan language"/>
